Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.74,0:00:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这是SimBrief的首页
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,顶部是主菜单
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Support是技术支持论坛
